---
import { ArrowRight } from '@lucide/astro'
---

<section class="relative pt-20 pb-20 lg:pt-20 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:gap-8">
    
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 z-10 text-center lg:text-left animate-fade-in-up">
      <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-sage text-sm font-semibold mb-6 tracking-wide uppercase">
        Gestion de Patrimoine
      </span>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl lg:text-7xl leading-tight text-sage mb-8">
Maîtrisez votre <span class="italic text-gold">avenir financier</span>, étape par étape.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-sage/70 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-relaxed">
        Des stratégies patrimoniales personnalisées pour les familles et les professionnels qui privilégient la clarté, la transparence et la croissance intergénérationnelle.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
        <button class="bg-primary text-background-dark font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl shadow-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center group cursor-pointer">
          Commencer votre parcours
          <ArrowRight class="ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform w-5 h-5" />
        </button>
        <button class="bg-white border border-sage/20 text-sage font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-beige transition-colors cursor-pointer">
          Nos Services
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:w-1/2 mt-16 lg:mt-0 relative animate-fade-in-scale opacity-0">
      <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-8 border-white">
        <img 
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/wealth/800/1000" 
          alt="Consultation avec un conseiller financier" 
          class="w-full h-125 object-cover"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div class="items-center space-x-4 hidden sm:flex">
            <div class="flex -space-x-2">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-200 border-2 border-white"></div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-300 border-2 border-white"></div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary border-2 border-white flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold text-white">+200</div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-sage">Plus de 200 familles nous font confiance</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Reproduction des animations Framer Motion en pur CSS */
  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
  }
  
  .animate-fade-in-scale {
    /* Le délai de 0.2s est ajouté ici */
    animation: fadeInScale 0.8s ease-out 0.2s forwards; 
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes fadeInScale {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.95);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }
</style>
